(0) READ-ITEM WORK-ARR JUMP TO (7) IF DATA-SEQUENCE-EXHAUSTED
(1) COMPARE WORK-ARR(I) TO MAXIMUM-VALUE JUMP TO (3) IF GREATER
(2) JUMP TO (4)
(3) STORE WORK-ARR(I) IN MAXIMUM-VALUE
(4) COMPUTE EXP-VALUE = EXP-VALUE * 10
(5) COMPARE EXP-VALUE DIV MAXIMUM-VALUE TO ZERO JUMP TO (9) IF EQUAL
(6) COMPUTE DIGIT = WORK-ARR(I) DIV EXP-VALUE
(7) COMPUTE DIGIT = DIGIT - DIGIT DIV 10 * 10
(8) COMPUTE COUNT(DIGIT) = COUNT(DIGIT) + 1
(9) WRITE-ITEM SORTED-OUTPUT STOP
